{"result": {"history_size": 1, "folders": ["q&a"], "nr": 1369, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "created": "2019-11-11T12:16:17Z", "bucket_order": 3, "no_answer_followup": 0, "change_log": [{"anon": "no", "uid": "jyheyxpma6o6k2", "data": "k2ue4y4r7hm1g7", "type": "create", "when": "2019-11-11T12:16:17Z"}, {"anon": "no", "uid": "jyheyxpma6o6k2", "to": "k2ue4y4q96b1g6", "type": "followup", "when": "2019-11-11T12:22:01Z"}], "bucket_name": "Today", "history": [{"anon": "no", "uid": "jyheyxpma6o6k2", "subject": "中断处理程序中被中断程序状态", "created": "2019-11-11T12:16:17Z", "content": "<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<div>因为个人水平有限&#xff0c;只是将大家的讨论汇总了一些&#xff0c;希望同学和老师能帮助归纳</div>\n<div>【问题提出】</div>\n<div>\n<div> &#64;loser<br />想问一下&#xff1a;运行的程序被外部中断打断进入中断处理程序&#xff0c;那么在中断处理程序中该进程算运行态还是阻塞态&#xff1f;</div>\n<div>【答案】运行态</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>【讨论过程】</div>\n<div>\n<div> &#64;libinyl<br />我觉得进程状态的改变并不应取决于中断  中断是控制权向内核的转移&#xff0c;与用户进程状态的改变无关。进程状态的改变取决于进程的特定操作&#xff0c;比如发起io等&#xff0c;以及idle的调度。trap只转移控制权&#xff0c;具体操作由handler决定</div>\n<div>&#64;Crowerly\n<div>中断是控制流的变换&#xff0c;阻塞态、运行态是进程的状态。该状态显然是可以由中断处理例程来修改的&#xff0c;如等待IO。也可能不会改变&#xff0c;如时钟中断的处理。</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>&#64;某普通大学的数学汪&#xff08;自学OS&#xff09;\n<div>中断以后还是原来的进程在运行&#xff0c;只是在运行中断代码</div>\n<div>&#64;libinyl\n<div>中断至少包含系统调用&#xff0c;系统调用通常包含io操作&#xff0c;io操作通常触发阻塞 </div>\n<div></div>\n<div>【向老师总结】</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div> &#64;向老师</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>中断响应不改变当前运行进程状态。 中断处理占用的CPU时间还算在当前进程的头上。</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>【再讨论】</div>\n<div>&#64;Fluray</div>\n<div>是的  current thread还是中断前的进程&#xff0c;中断结束后一般会有调度的判断。如果允许抢占并且有高优先级的线程 则直接调度到高优先级线程上 </div>\n<div>\n<div>&#64;libinyl</div>\n<div>一般不会有吧&#xff1f;调度判断应由idle线程负责&#xff1f;</div>\n<div>&#64;向老师</div>\n<div>\n<div>时钟中断的响应就是一个例子</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div></div>"}], "type": "note", "tags": ["q&a", "student"], "tag_good": [], "unique_views": 101, "children": [{"anon": "no", "folders": [], "data": {"embed_links": null}, "no_upvotes": 0, "subject": "<p>个人觉得这张图解释了核心问题&#xff0c;出处是某辅导机构&#xff0c;来源不明</p>\n<p></p>\n<p><img src=\"/img/1369-1e9a1e2d7648aee9.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>", "created": "2019-11-11T12:22:01Z", "bucket_order": 114, "bucket_name": "Week 11/10 - 11/16", "type": "followup", "tag_good": [], "uid": "jyheyxpma6o6k2", "children": [], "tag_good_arr": [], "no_answer": 0, "id": "k2uecbf2cxg615", "updated": "2019-11-11T12:22:01Z", "config": {}}], "tag_good_arr": [], "id": "k2ue4y4q96b1g6", "config": {}, "status": "active", "drafts": null, "request_instructor": 0, "request_instructor_me": false, "bookmarked": 1, "num_favorites": 1, "my_favorite": false, "is_bookmarked": false, "is_tag_good": false, "q_edits": [], "i_edits": [], "s_edits": [], "t": 1643169851471, "default_anonymity": "no"}, "error": null, "aid": "kyv0wjtbsy31c6"}